ULAHLWE yicala lokubulala uMbhishobhi waseZayoni, eManguzi obethathwa njengobhongoza etulweni lokubulala kucwiywe uNksz Thandazile Nanana Msweli owayenebala elimhlophe waseScabazini, KwaMhlabuyalingana ngo-2015. UMbhishobhi uBhekukufa Gumede (67) ulahlwe yiNkantolo eNkulu yaseMtubatuba izolo kanti kulindeleke ukuthi agwetshwe namuhla. Ngesikhathi ijaji uThemba Sishi limlahla ngecala lithe umbuso ulethe ubufakazi obungangabazeki usebenzisa izitatimende zasebegwetshiwe ngaleli cala oMandla Mabuza, Lindokuhle Khumalo noSiyabonga Gwala abaveze ukuthi babethunywe nguGumede ukuthi babulale umufi. Bazivumela bona ukuthi babulala uNksz Msweli bagwetshwa iminyaka engu-15 umuntu ngamunye. USishi uthe ubufakazi obethulwe enkantolo buyakuveza ukuthi uGumede wayekhona kwenziwa icala futhi enenhloso ngayekwenza. Uthe ubufakazi obethulwe enkantolo buveza ukuthi uGumede wahlangana nalaba abanye. USishi uthe obunye ubufakazi bukaGumede bungamampunge njengoba athi washaywa amaphoyisa esitokisini. Uthe into engacaci wukuthi uGumede wayekhona yini ngesikhathi kubulawa umuntu kodwa kuyacaca ukuthi uyathinteka etulweni lokubulala. Ngokobufakazi obethulwe enkantolo uGumede wahlangana noMabuza wamcela ukuba athole umuntu wesifazane onebala elimhlophe ozobulawa acwiywe ukuze kwakhiwe umuthi wokuceba ngezicubu zakhe. Kuvele ukuthi wayemthembise uR25 000. UMabuza waluxoxela umzala wakhe uKhumalo lolu daba bakha isu lokuthola owesifazane. Bathola uGwala owaqonywa ngumufi owaphuma kubo ngosuku abulawa ngalo ngoba ebizwe yisoka lakhe. Kuvele ukuthi babamba umufi bamsonta intamo bamgwaza wafa base bebiza uGumede owafika ngemoto yakhe eyiveni wathatha isidumbu. Sebehamba ngemoto babona imoto yamaphoyisa bangena ehlathini bahlinza isidumbu. Ubufakazi obuthulwe enkantolo buveza ukuthi uGumede wasika isitho sangasese nesandla wahlinza nesikhumba wahamba nakho. Ezinye izitho zomzimba ezingasebenzanga zafakwa ebhakedeni zagqitshwa eduze komgwaqo iPhelandaba. Sekuzwakele ukuthi kukhona owesifazane olahlekile, uMabuza, Khumalo noGwala baya emzini kaGumede beyofuna imali ayebathembise yona nomuthi wokugquma ukuze bangabonakali kodwa wabanika uR200 wokuthi babaleke endaweni. UGumede wathi lobu bufakazi bungamanga.Unina kamufi, uNksz Khanyisile Masinga, uthe ufisa agwetshwe udilikajele uGumede ngoba yamhlukumeza into ayenza enganeni yakhe.